commit_message:
Added a scoring method based on Doench 2016 paper

Added a scoring method that provides sgRNA efficiency scores based on a gradient boosted regression model. This model is trained on the data from the Doench 2016 paper and uses similar settings.

Removed TTTT homopolymer calling

Having a separate data column for TTTT homopolymers is unnecessary
Fixed bugs related to custom PAM option

Added optional PAM site argument

Added a user interface option to use a custom PAM

Finished rewriting for custom PAMS

Allowed a single variable to be set to change the PAM site the program searches for

Started custom PAM work

Started to rewrite code to allow custom PAMs

Fixed off-target search bug

Fixed a bug that prevented off-target hits from appearing in the off-target table

Added self complementary detection

Added the ability to detect sgRNA sequences that may form hairpins with themselves or the RNA backbone

Fixed off-target searching bug

Corrected method of off-target searching so that it considers the PAM separate from the target sequence.

Added .txt file functionality

Now able to use .txt files for target sequences

Bug fixes

Fixed Bugs related to the .gtf selection and additional options.

Bug fixes and .gtf selection

Fixed a bug that kept the off-target annotation from loading and allowed users to input the name of a .gtf file to use.

Removed email and added options

Removed the unnecessary email functionality and fixed bugs related to the additional options
Added references to the crispRdesignR package
